The paper deals with the problem of detecting AI-synthesized face swapping videos, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms for detecting DeepFakes, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper discusses the technical aspects of generating the Celeb-DF dataset, which could fall under the category of cryptography and security (cs.CR).
